#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque PJMBUD1T0 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:05:45"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230545"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask PJMBUD1T0 [PJBU10]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "PJMBUD1T0" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [PJBU10] As [SIM_]
Grizo [PJBU10]10
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [PJBU10]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=113 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=25
Return

$ON_PBUCOD
Return

$ON_CUR
Return

$ON_UOM
Return

$ON_ZUOM
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZUOM From W1PJMBUD1T0
Return

$AV_ZUOM
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"TABUNIT","DES",num$([M]UOM(indice)),"") From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

$CHG_STY
Return


